- and these guys back here...
- Andy.

1197
01:18:44,570 --> 01:18:46,697
Really.
Who gives a shit?

1198
01:18:46,772 --> 01:18:51,709
- Do you want to tell me what happened?
- Beat it, Andy.

1199
01:19:00,486 --> 01:19:02,420
Andy.

1200
01:19:02,488 --> 01:19:04,422
What'd you do?
<font color="#D900D9">(LAUGHS)</font>

1201
01:19:16,369 --> 01:19:20,465
- Can I buy you a drink?
- Yeah, I'd love one.

1202
01:19:22,575 --> 01:19:24,941
Sit down.

1203
