1262
01:23:26,752 --> 01:23:28,720
My dad gave it to me
for my birthday.

1263
01:23:28,787 --> 01:23:30,687
Yeah?

1264
01:23:30,756 --> 01:23:32,849
What were you going
to do with me?

1265
01:23:32,925 --> 01:23:35,450
I hadn't really worked
that part out yet.

1266
01:23:35,527 --> 01:23:37,722
All I knew is that I liked you,
and that I didn't wanna...

1267
01:23:37,796 --> 01:23:40,316
leave you there on the side of the road
and never see you again.

1268
01:23:41,634 --> 01:23:43,602
Then you waved to me
in that elevator.

1269
01:23:43,669 --> 01:23:46,570
- Yeah, I wasn't sure if you caught that.
- <font color="#D900D9">(LAUGHS)</font>

1270
01:23:46,639 --> 01:23:49,665
I couldn't believe it.
By that time I had been...

1271
01:23:49,742 --> 01:23:51,972
thinking about you a lot...

1272
01:23:52,044 --> 01:23:55,502
and just wondering
what it would be like if we met,

1273
01:23:55,581 --> 01:23:58,607
if we could take a time-out.

1274
01:23:58,684 --> 01:24:01,050
I was thinking the same thing.

1275
01:24:01,120 --> 01:24:03,987
I kept thinking,
"What if we took a time-out?"

1276
01:24:04,056 --> 01:24:07,924
If we... just spent
some time together.

1277
01:24:12,765 --> 01:24:14,699
- You know, I saw you on the street.
- Where?

1278
01:24:14,767 --> 01:24:17,258
Outside Adele's.

1279
01:24:17,336 --> 01:24:20,203
- You went to see her?
- To warn her about Chino.

1280
01:24:20,272 --> 01:24:23,503
- So she did help you.
- I don't think we should get into that.

1281
01:24:23,575 --> 01:24:25,634
You're right.
And I won't ask about Buddy,

1282
01:24:25,711 --> 01:24:31,240
or what you guys are doing in Detroit, or
if you've run into Glenn Michaels yet...

1283
01:24:31,317 --> 01:24:34,150
Okay, now, don't talk like that,
because you scare me.

1284
01:24:45,831 --> 01:24:48,800
- Let's get out of here.
- Yeah.

1285
01:25:43,155 --> 01:25:45,783
There's something
I want you to know.

1286
01:25:45,858 --> 01:25:48,122
I wasn't just looking for a fuck,
if that's what you're thinking.

1287
01:25:48,193 --> 01:25:50,821
- Or, I was...
- Why are you mad?

1288
01:25:50,896 --> 01:25:54,491
I was looking for some kinky thrill...
you know, score with the bank robber.

1289
01:25:54,566 --> 01:25:57,330
- The way some women go for rough trade...
- All right.

1290
01:25:57,403 --> 01:26:01,396
Now I can say that I fucked
a U.S. Marshal. Do you think I will?

1291
01:26:01,473 --> 01:26:03,703
I don't know.

1292
01:26:03,776 --> 01:26:05,710
Mm-hmm.

1293
01:26:07,312 --> 01:26:09,246
Come here.

1294
01:26:21,627 --> 01:26:24,095
I know a guy...

1295
01:26:24,163 --> 01:26:27,257
