tells everybody it's nitroglycerine.

1296
01:26:27,332 --> 01:26:29,926
He scores some cash
off of the teller.

1297
01:26:30,002 --> 01:26:33,301
On his way out, he drops the bottle.
It cracks on the floor.

1298
01:26:33,372 --> 01:26:37,001
He slips in it. He smacks up
his head. They get him.

1299
01:26:37,076 --> 01:26:40,773
The nitroglycerine
was canola oil.

1300
01:26:40,846 --> 01:26:44,577
I know more fucked-up bank robbers
than ones that know what they're doing.

1301
01:26:44,650 --> 01:26:48,814
I doubt one in ten could tell you
where the dye pack is.

1302
01:26:48,887 --> 01:26:51,412
Most bank robbers
are fucking morons.

1303
01:26:51,490 --> 01:26:55,927
For you to go to bed with one
for kinky thrills,

1304
01:26:55,994 --> 01:26:59,327
like you were saying,
makes you as dumb as they are.

1305
01:26:59,398 --> 01:27:01,332
Now, you are not dumb.

1306
01:27:03,202 --> 01:27:07,901
Why would you think that? Why would
you think that I would think that?

1307
01:27:11,110 --> 01:27:13,078
You're not dumb.

1308
01:27:14,913 --> 01:27:17,074
Well, I don't know about that.
<font color="#D900D9">(LAUGHS)</font>

1309
01:27:17,149 --> 01:27:20,243
