and think you have much of a brain.

1310
01:27:21,720 --> 01:27:23,654
Come here.

1311
01:27:41,306 --> 01:27:43,501
You're getting
serious on me now.

1312
01:27:46,545 --> 01:27:48,740
Tryin' not to.

1313
01:27:51,817 --> 01:27:54,217
I just want to know
what's gonna happen.

1314
01:28:01,360 --> 01:28:03,294
You know.

1315
01:28:53,145 --> 01:28:55,477
Put it together now. Put it together!
Upstairs and downstairs.

1316
01:28:55,547 --> 01:28:58,516
- He don't want to see you downstairs!
- Man, you drink like a bitch!

1317
01:29:00,285 --> 01:29:02,845
He don't want to see you... Get your
tussle on. Joe, get your tussle on!

1318
01:29:02,921 --> 01:29:05,253
Yeah, don't let him
out that corner.

1319
01:29:05,324 --> 01:29:07,519
Don't let him out, now.

1320
01:29:10,128 --> 01:29:13,586
Hey, you know what?
I gotta go take a pee.

