the jewels at, Dick?

1541
01:46:52,123 --> 01:46:54,226
Foley... Foley's got them.
Go after Foley!

1542
01:46:54,251 --> 01:46:55,913
Where the fuck is Foley, man?

1543
01:47:03,034 --> 01:47:04,968
Midge?

1544
01:47:11,008 --> 01:47:13,340
- Midge!
- Sit your punk ass down, man.

1545
01:47:14,578 --> 01:47:17,103
- Ooh, goddamn!
- Son of a bitch!

1546
01:47:17,181 --> 01:47:20,582
Man, take the front stairs.
I'm gonna take the back.

1547
01:47:23,321 --> 01:47:26,154
- You all right?
- Where's Richard?

1548
01:47:26,223 --> 01:47:29,920
He's downstairs.
You wait here.

1549
01:47:34,932 --> 01:47:38,629
Hold it, asshole.
Drop the gun.

1550
01:47:39,904 --> 01:47:41,838
Drop it!

1551
01:47:41,906 --> 01:47:43,965
Put the damn gun down, now.

1552
01:47:45,142 --> 01:47:47,906
Now!

1553
01:47:47,978 --> 01:47:51,106
Put it down!

1554
01:47:54,285 --> 01:47:57,379
Stay right there.
Don't move. Maurice!

1555
01:47:57,455 --> 01:47:59,389
I got Foley!

1556
01:48:01,892 --> 01:48:03,826
Maurice!

1557
01:48:34,291 --> 01:48:37,055
<font color="#D900D9">(LAUGHING)</font> Ain't got
another clip I can use, do you?

1558
01:48:37,128 --> 01:48:39,426
No, I don't.

1559
01:48:41,966 --> 01:48:44,140
You ain't never shot a
gun before, have you?

1560
01:48:44,165 --> 01:48:45,517
Not until recently, no.

1561
01:48:45,569 --> 01:48:48,003
- You a little nervous?
- Little bit, yeah.

1562
01:48:48,072 --> 01:48:52,668
You know, a situation like this
has a high potentiality...

1563
01:48:52,743 --> 01:48:54,677
for the common motherfucker
to bitch out.

1564
01:48:54,745 --> 01:48:57,509
- So I figure, why take a chance?
- <font color="#D900D9">(GUN CLICKS)</font>

1565
01:48:59,417 --> 01:49:01,351
Bitch!

1566
01:49:03,921 --> 01:49:05,855
- Aw, sh...!
- Motherfucker!

1567
01:49:41,158 --> 01:49:43,217
Stop! Put your hands in the air!

1568
01:49:59,877 --> 01:50:01,811
Jack?

1569
01:50:03,280 --> 01:50:06,477
- I know you're up there.
- Shit!

1570
01:50:09,620 --> 01:50:12,521
- Where's Kenneth?
- He's up here.

1571
01:50:14,825 --> 01:50:17,157
He's dead.

1572
01:50:38,415 --> 01:50:42,146
- Come on, Jack, don't.
- Pretend it's not me.

1573
01:50:42,219 --> 01:50:45,347
- You think I'd shoot you?
- If you don't, somebody else will.

1574
01:50:45,422 --> 01:50:49,085
What're you now?
A desperado?

1575
01:50:49,159 --> 01:50:53,220
- Put the gun down.
- I'm not goin' back.

1576
01:50:55,266 --> 01:50:59,498
Jack, please, don't make me do this.
Put the gun down.

1577
01:51:02,273 --> 01:51:07,301
- Damn it, Jack, put the gun down!
- <font color="#D900D9">(SIRENS IN DISTANCE)</font>

1578
01:51:07,378 --> 01:51:09,312
No more time-outs.

1579
01:51:18,589 --> 01:51:21,319
You win, Jack.

1580
01:51:29,800 --> 01:51:33,258
- I can't shoot you.
- You did. You shot me.

1581
01:51:33,337 --> 01:51:35,567
You know what I mean.

1582
01:51:49,086 --> 01:51:53,648
I'm sorry.
I wish things were different.

1583
01:52:36,800 --> 01:52:38,734
Airport.

1584
01:53:05,863 --> 01:53:09,663
<font color="#808080">KAREN:</font> Yeah, they don't know yet if they
want to bring him up on the homicides.

1585
01:53:09,733 --> 01:53:12,566
I doubt if they will.
They'll just put a detainer on him.

1586
01:53:12,636 --> 01:53:15,605
When they're through with him here,
he'll go back to Florida.

1587
01:53:15,673 --> 01:53:18,005
<font color="#808080">MR. SISKO:</font>
Are you gonna go get him?

1588
01:53:18,075 --> 01:53:20,305
It's possible. Why?

1589
01:53:20,377 --> 01:53:22,311
Well, you know,
I was just thinkin'.

1590
01:53:22,379 --> 01:53:24,379
You can have a nice time
with him on the ride down,

1591
01:53:24,381 --> 01:53:27,373
picking up where your interlude
or whatever you call it left off,

1592
01:53:27,451 --> 01:53:30,284
and then you can throw him
in the shithouse.

1593
01:53:31,789 --> 01:53:34,019
<font color="#808080">KAREN:</font>
He knew what he was doing.

1594
01:53:34,091 --> 01:53:36,992
Nobody forced him to rob banks.

1595
01:53:38,262 --> 01:53:42,096
<font color="#808080">MR. SISKO:</font>
My little girl... the tough babe.

1596
01:53:42,166 --> 01:53:44,100
<font color="#808080">KAREN:</font>
I'll call you later.

1597
01:53:44,168 --> 01:53:46,329
<font color="#808080">MR. SISCO:</font>
Good-bye.

1598
01:54:03,721 --> 01:54:05,985
Jack.

1599
01:54:08,559 --> 01:54:10,493
I got you a present.

1600
01:54:13,263 --> 01:54:15,288
Something for the road.

1601
01:54:27,277 --> 01:54:31,907
I'm gonna have to take it away,
though, soon as the ride is over.

1602
01:54:44,595 --> 01:54:47,496
Jack Foley?
Meet Hijirah Henry.

1603
01:54:58,208 --> 01:55:00,142
What kind of a name is Hijirah?

1604
01:55:00,210 --> 01:55:03,668
- It's Islamic.
- What's it stand for?

1605
01:55:03,747 --> 01:55:07,183
The "Hijirah" was Mohammed's
flight from Mecca in 622.

1606
01:55:07,251 --> 01:55:08,143
His flight?

1607
01:55:08,168 --> 01:55:11,735
Brothers in Leavenworth
gave me that name.

1608
01:55:11,789 --> 01:55:13,723
You were in Leavenworth, huh?

1609
01:55:13,791 --> 01:55:16,760
- Four time.
- Meaning?

1610
01:55:16,827 --> 01:55:19,853
- Meaning, time came, I left.
- You busted out.

1611
01:55:19,930 --> 01:55:23,457
I prefer to think of it as an exodus
from an undesirable place.

1612
01:55:26,770 --> 01:55:29,102
- How long before they caught up with you?
- That time?

1613
01:55:31,375 --> 01:55:34,708
- There were others?
- Yeah. That was the ninth.

1614
01:55:36,713 --> 01:55:39,181
The ninth?

1615
01:55:39,249 --> 01:55:43,049
Well, ten if you count that prison
hospital in Ohio I walked away from.

1616
01:55:43,120 --> 01:55:45,918
- You done a lot of walkin', Henry.
- Hijirah.

1617
01:55:45,989 --> 01:55:49,356
Hijirah.
Now we're off to Glades.

1618
01:55:49,426 --> 01:55:53,556
Yeah, it looks that way.

1619
01:55:53,630 --> 01:55:56,360
I was supposed to leave
last night with the lady marshal,

1620
01:55:56,433 --> 01:55:59,800
but for some reason
she wanted to wait.

1621
01:55:59,870 --> 01:56:00,650
She did, huh?

1622
01:56:00,675 --> 01:56:03,796
Guess it's cheaper taking
two of us down in one van.

1623
01:56:03,841 --> 01:56:09,074
Could be. Maybe she thought
we had a lot to talk about.

1624
01:56:09,146 --> 01:56:11,205
Really? Like what?

1625
01:56:12,883 --> 01:56:17,547
I don't know.
Long ride to Florida.

